                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for component adaptive energy conversion and element reforming linkage during combustion of hydrogen, carbon, nitrogen and oxygen",
                    "燃烧氢碳氮氧时组分适配能量转换与元素重整结链的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for realizing element reforming by a component adaptive energy conversion system during combustion of hydrogen, carbon, nitrogen and oxygen. According to the invention, air flows through a diaphragm, oxygen-enriched and nitrogen elements are separated in a low-power-consumption manner through differential pressure, after oxygen-enriched and hydrogen-carbon substances are combusted by a combustor under high temperature and pressure, gas expansion jet work and slowly released heat energy are utilized in a closed manner and converted into electromechanical energy to be output outwards, and a small amount of unconverted waste heat is conveyed into a storage device to be called at night or at low temperature; the tail gas is subjected to treatment such as cleaning, desulfurization and nitre adhesion with carbonitride, and unconverted carbon oxide, carbon-nitrogen compound, nitrogen and gas heat are conveyed to the three-dimensional greenhouse; the concentration of carbon oxide is intelligently adjusted to 410-4500 ppm, heat is applied as a main light source to assist in combined action for carbon and nitrogen fixation and high-speed growth and metabolism of pasture, vegetables, fruits, forests, grains and crops in the three-dimensional greenhouse, forest and agricultural vegetables are provided for people, poultry and animals to use, part of exhaled air is recycled, and friendly recycling of hydrogen, carbon, nitrogen and oxygen is achieved through the method."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种燃烧氢碳氮氧时组分适配能量转换系统实现元素重整的方法。本发明是将空气流经隔膜压差低功耗分离出富氧与氮元素，燃烧器以富氧与氢碳物质在高温、压下燃烧后，燃气膨胀喷射功，慢速释放的热能闭合利用转换为机电能对外输出，未转化的少量余热输往储存装置内供夜间或低温时调用，尾气清洗脱硫硝黏连碳氮化物等处理，未转化的氧化碳、炭氮化合物、氮、气热输往立体大棚；将氧化碳浓度智能化调整到410‑4500ppm，同时施以热为主光源辅助联合作用供立体大棚内牧草蔬菜水果林木粮农作物固碳氮、高速生长代谢，林农蔬产获提供给人、家禽、动物利用，呼出的部分空气循环再用，本发明方法实现了氢碳氮氧的友好再循环。"
                }
            ]
